<<set-title "SahrisWiki ChangesLog">>

= Change Log =
//SahrisWiki ChangeLog//

== 0.8 ==
* [+]: The page index (//searching for nothing//) now lists a tree
* [+]: Can now search for specific pages (//not just words//)
* [!]: --daemon now works
* [!]: --readonly now works
* [+]: Added support to specify logfile (//--logfile//)
* [+]: Rudimentary user authentication support
** Uses HTTP Basic Auth
** Default username/password == admin/admin (//use --password to change//)
** Uses htpasswd style file (//use --htpasswd//)
* [+]: Many new configuration options (//See sahriswiki --help//)
** Options to disable compression, static, hgweb and logging
** Options to set baseurl for static resources
** //And many more...//
* [+]: Subdirectory Storage with Indexes (//now the default//).
* [ ]: Initial public documentation of changes: [[<<title>>]]
----

**Legend:**
* [+] Addition of something new.
* [-] Removal of an existing feature.
* [!] Fix of an existing broken feature.
* [ ] Uncategorized
